Package com.onarandombox.multiverseinventories.share

Class Sharables

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onarandombox.multiverseinventories.share.Sharables
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shares, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Sharable>, java.util.Collection<Sharable>, java.util.Set<Sharable>
    public final class Sharables
extends java.lang.Object
implements Shares
    The Sharables class is where all the default Sharable instances are located as constants as well as a factory class for generating Shares.
